a \otimes b =\sum_{i} (a^i b^i)(e_i \otimes e_i) + \sum_{i \neq j} (a^i b^j) (e_i \otimes e_j)
a b = a \cdot b + a \wedge b = \sum_i a^i b^i + \sum_{i \neq j} a^i b^j (e_i \wedge e_j)
